  <h1>单晶硅</h1>
  <h3>来源</h3>
  <text>
    <style color="0xaaaaaa" italic="true" pwt="true">注释：本页转载于MCMOD的GTCEu维基<br/>作者：<style color="0xa4e7ff" hover-info="url" pwt="true" underlined="true" url-link="https://center.mcmod.cn/179043/">花海</style>，<style color="0xa4e7ff" hover-info="url" pwt="true" underlined="true" url-link="https://center.mcmod.cn/508290/">morningglory</style>，<style color="0xa4e7ff" hover-info="url" underlined="true" url-link="https://github.com/Yefancy">KilaBash</style><br/>，<style color="0xa4e7ff" hover-info="url" underlined="true" url-link="https://github.com/blackdragon2447">BlackDragon2447</style><br/></style>
  </text>
  <h2>合成和用途</h2>
  <text>单晶硅是由32个<style color="0xbbffaa">硅粉</style>和一小堆<style color="0xbbffaa">砷化镓粉</style>在<style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:multiblock/electric_blast_furnace" underlined="true">电力高炉</style>中熔炼而成的，需要<style color="0xff5555">1,784 K</style>的最低线圈温度才能完成合成，这只需要白铜线圈即可熔炼。</text>
  <recipe id="gtceu:electric_blast_furnace/silicon_boule"></recipe>
  <br/>
  <text>在<style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:machines/cutter" underlined="true">切割机</style>中，可将一块单晶硅切割成16片<style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:circuits/wafers" underlined="true">硅晶圆</style>，最低需要MV电压处理。</text>
  <recipe id="gtceu:cutter/cut_silicon_boule_water"></recipe>
  <br/>
  <h2>掺杂技术</h2>
  <text>单晶硅可以掺杂各种材料，其<style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:circuits/wafers" underlined="true">晶圆</style>是更高级电路所必需的。这些晶圆需要在<style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:multiblock/cleanroom" underlined="true">超净间</style>内切割。用于掺杂晶圆的材料依次为：</text>
  <br/>
  <h3>磷</h3>
  <text>这些硅棒可在HV下生产、切割和刻蚀，并需要在<style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:multiblock/electric_blast_furnace" underlined="true">电力高炉</style>中使用氮气作为保护气。</text>
  <recipe id="gtceu:electric_blast_furnace/phosphorus_boule"></recipe>
  <recipe id="gtceu:cutter/cut_phosphorus_boule_water"></recipe>
  <h3>硅岩</h3>
  <text>这些硅棒可在EV下生产、切割和刻蚀，并需要在<style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:multiblock/electric_blast_furnace" underlined="true">电力高炉</style>中使用氩气作为保护气。</text>
  <recipe id="gtceu:electric_blast_furnace/naquadah_boule"></recipe>
  <recipe id="gtceu:cutter/cut_naquadah_boule_water"></recipe>
  <h3>中子素</h3>
  <text>这些硅棒可在IV下生产、切割和刻蚀，并需要在<style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:multiblock/electric_blast_furnace" underlined="true">电力高炉</style>中使用氙气作为保护气。</text>
  <recipe id="gtceu:electric_blast_furnace/neutronium_boule"></recipe>
  <recipe id="gtceu:cutter/cut_neutronium_boule_water"></recipe>
</page>
